{
  "stem": "8892.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when we got off the train, I don't know what my cousin expected, but we had normal Western clothes already from Sweden, you know, hat, purse, coat, everything, except no makeup.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My cousin still wouldn't let me put nothing on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right away.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The next morning-- the next day they put us to the train to Detroit, and I'm in Detroit since then.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I arrived to Detroit, right away, about two, three-- two weeks, I think-- my uncles, who I call uncle.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They are.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But Uncle Dave had a store in downtown, and he would take me-- the only-- the school was open daytime for English was all the way across from the city hall, way down downtown.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In those days, they lived on Dexter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I would take-- he would take me for at least a week.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after that, every morning, showed up at my aunt's house, picked me up, and took me to school.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Magda just stayed around the house, you know, with my aunt because she didn't want to go in a day school.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't even know why, but she didn't.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I wanted.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So after a week or so, I said to my uncle, oh no, I'm big enough, and I understand enough that I'm going to go take the bus on myself alone.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So sure enough, I took the bus, and I'm going on a bus, going, so I thought I'm already downtown.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I get off on Grand Boulevard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] After that, I learned how to get there by myself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I went to school all that summer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my cousin, who is in Caracas now-- see, the family came together and it was Pesach.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A week later, it was Passover.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
